mgI18nPlugin
============

This plugin add an extra option "Translation" in the debug web panel. This panel allow the user to update the translation on the current page.

Requirements
------------

* symfony 1.2
* doctrine 
* jQuery
* swToolboxPlugin (http://www.symfony-project.org/plugins/swToolboxPlugin)

Installation
------------

 * edit your factories.yml 

        [yml]            
        all:
          # ...
          i18n:
            class: mgI18N
            param:
              source:               mgMySQL
              database:             mysql://user:password@127.0.0.1/database_i18n
              encoding:             utf8
              debug:                off
              untranslated_prefix:  "[T]"
              untranslated_suffix:  "[/T]"
              cache:
                class: sfFileCache
                param:
                  automatic_cleaning_factor: 0
                  cache_dir:                 %SF_I18N_CACHE_DIR%
                  lifetime:                  86400
                  prefix:                    %SF_APP_DIR%

 * you can change the default doctrine connection's name by editing your app.yml file

        [yml]
        all:
          # ...
          mgI18nPlugin:
            connection: doctrine # default is mg_i18n_plugin
            culture_available: 
              fr: Fran√ßais
              en: English

 * enable the mgI18nAdmin module from your backend application

Note
----

You can import xliff catalogue with the command : 

        [php]
        ./symfony mgI18n:xliff-import frontend PATH_TO_YOUR_CATALOGUES/*|YOUR_CATALOGUE
